1286
00:41:54,911 --> 00:41:58,280
What's the second largest island in Korea?

1287
00:41:58,281 --> 00:41:59,420
The second largest island?

1288
00:41:59,421 --> 00:42:01,651
Yeouido? Isn't that also an island?

1289
00:42:01,951 --> 00:42:02,991
Yeouido is also an island.

1290
00:42:03,151 --> 00:42:04,921
The answer is Geoje Island.

1291
00:42:05,091 --> 00:42:06,320
