1311
00:42:37,791 --> 00:42:39,761
What's this?

1312
00:42:42,761 --> 00:42:44,801
(He tries to move the turning point.)

1313
00:42:45,531 --> 00:42:46,531
Gosh.

1314
00:42:46,532 --> 00:42:47,647
