1319
00:42:54,411 --> 00:42:55,871
I weigh 126kg.

1320
00:42:56,371 --> 00:42:58,181
I weigh 126kg. How much do you weigh?

1321
00:42:58,611 --> 00:43:00,041
This is exhausting.

1322
00:43:00,681 --> 00:43:03,250
Dear viewers, I weigh 126kg.

1323
00:43:03,251 --> 00:43:04,327
