1324
00:43:04,351 --> 00:43:07,081
This is killing me. It's so brutal.

1325
00:43:07,851 --> 00:43:08,851
Joon.

1326
00:43:09,791 --> 00:43:12,067
Arriving first makes no difference. I don't know the answer.

1327
00:43:12,091 --> 00:43:13,291
Darn it.

1328
00:43:13,791 --> 00:43:16,631
