1329
00:43:16,791 --> 00:43:18,631
Why do we have to wear this?

1330
00:43:19,031 --> 00:43:20,131
I'm taking it off.

1331
00:43:20,161 --> 00:43:21,571
I can only hear them moan.

1332
00:43:22,001 --> 00:43:24,200
