1356
00:44:10,851 --> 00:44:11,931
I know a lot about science.

1357
00:44:12,221 --> 00:44:14,661
(He has to go back again without getting a chance to answer.)

1358
00:44:14,751 --> 00:44:16,751
(They give up and set off right away.)

1359
00:44:16,851 --> 00:44:18,260
- I'm good at science.
- Really?

1360
00:44:18,261 --> 00:44:19,261
I know a lot about planets.

1361
00:44:19,262 --> 00:44:20,491
Isn't it "Aurora?"

1362
00:44:21,091 --> 00:44:22,190
Princess Aurora.

1363
00:44:22,191 --> 00:44:23,191
(He still can't give up.)

1364
00:44:23,192 --> 00:44:24,330
Isn't there Princess Aurora in the mythology?

1365
00:44:24,331 --> 00:44:25,931
Oh, dear. I made it.

1366
00:44:26,731 --> 00:44:27,970
