1390
00:45:14,751 --> 00:45:16,051
Hippocrates.

1391
00:45:17,411 --> 00:45:18,921
- Right?
- Aurora.

1392
00:45:19,351 --> 00:45:20,480
Androida.

1393
00:45:20,481 --> 00:45:21,690
Android.

1394
00:45:21,691 --> 00:45:23,397
