- Jong Min, show us what you've got.
- Something's coming out.

1396
00:45:25,221 --> 00:45:26,621
Something's coming out of my mouth.

1397
00:45:26,991 --> 00:45:28,960
- Here goes the next question.
- Give us an easy one.

1398
00:45:28,961 --> 00:45:29,961
Give us an easy one.

1399
00:45:30,861 --> 00:45:33,260
In the pansori "Chunhyangga,"

