1410
00:45:53,821 --> 00:45:55,850
Ssukdaemeori

1411
00:45:55,851 --> 00:45:57,250
Tell us the result so that we can leave.

1412
00:45:57,251 --> 00:45:58,260
(Being sure it's the correct answer, he's singing again to celebrate.)

1413
00:45:58,261 --> 00:45:59,991
Young Master

1414
