Although it's very foggy now...

1429
00:46:33,361 --> 00:46:35,691
Do you know the second largest island in Korea?

1430
00:46:36,061 --> 00:46:37,590
The second largest island in Korea?

1431
00:46:37,591 --> 00:46:38,660
