Oh, I know. Yeouido.

1433
00:46:40,631 --> 00:46:43,571
See? He said the same answer as me. He's not so different from me.

1434
00:46:44,071 --> 00:46:45,900
It's a difficult one. They wouldn't get it right.

1435
00:46:45,901 --> 00:46:47,201
