- That's right.

1476
00:48:05,451 --> 00:48:07,571
- My legs hurt. I'll take a break.
- You've got this!

1477
00:48:08,151 --> 00:48:09,490
You've got this!

1478
00:48:09,491 --> 00:48:11,421
(He puts his plan into action.)

1479
00:48:12,291 --> 00:48:14,361
(He succeeds in stealing.)

1480
00:48:15,791 --> 00:48:17,191
(The saddle thief)

1481
00:48:19,301 --> 00:48:20,607
