1499
00:48:53,631 --> 00:48:54,900
You can get this one right.

1500
00:48:54,901 --> 00:48:56,330
- Let's get it right first.
- You can get it right.

1501
00:48:56,331 --> 00:48:57,331
(Squabbling)

1502
00:48:57,332 --> 00:48:58,901
Here goes your question.

1503
00:48:59,371 --> 00:49:01,871
In one of Korea's best novels...

1504
00:49:02,271 --> 00:49:04,340
- "The Tale of Hong Gil Dong,"
- "The Tale of Hong Gil Dong."

1505
00:49:04,341 --> 00:49:05,341
