2562
01:24:09,540 --> 01:24:10,839
- It's delicious.
- It's good, isn't it?

2563
01:24:10,840 --> 01:24:11,840
It's great.

2564
01:24:12,040 --> 01:24:13,510
It must be delicious.

2565
01:24:13,980 --> 01:24:15,179
Who wants the scallop?

2566
01:24:15,180 --> 01:24:18,620
