2570
01:24:24,120 --> 01:24:25,149
I like it.

2571
01:24:25,150 --> 01:24:29,529
(After feeding the members, Se Yoon tries the scallop.)

2572
01:24:29,530 --> 01:24:31,660
- The scallops are a bit small.
- Yes.

2573
01:24:31,690 --> 01:24:34,299
But the scent and flavor are concentrated.

2574
01:24:34,300 --> 01:24:36,329
(Though they're small, they pack a concentrated flavor and scent.)

2575
01:24:36,330 --> 01:24:37,800
It's so chewy.

2576
01:24:38,640 --> 01:24:39,939
I'm cooking ramyeon now.

2577
01:24:39,940 --> 01:24:42,040
