2594
01:25:18,270 --> 01:25:22,310
(Noodle-eater Jong Min takes a big slurp too.)

2595
01:25:23,150 --> 01:25:25,010
(This is it.)

2596
01:25:25,150 --> 01:25:26,619
This is crazy. It's so good.

2597
01:25:26,620 --> 01:25:28,149
How can ramyeon be so good?

2598
01:25:28,150 --> 01:25:29,589
(You can never get tired of eating ramyeon.)

2599
01:25:29,590 --> 01:25:30,850
It's the best food.

2600
01:25:32,360 --> 01:25:34,789
Ramyeon is so good when you are out and about.

2601
01:25:34,790 --> 01:25:36,889
Right. I eat ramyeon like this when I'm outside.

2602
01:25:36,890 --> 01:25:39,050
(The taste of blowing on noodles in the cold outdoors)

2603
01:25:39,500 --> 01:25:43,230
(The seafood in the ramyeon is also exquisite.)

2604
01:25:43,430 --> 01:25:44,799
Try it with the murex.

2605
01:25:44,800 --> 01:25:46,069
(Premium ramyeon packed with seafood)

2606
01:25:46,070 --> 01:25:48,040
- This is fancy ramyeon.
- This is like samhap.

2607
01:25:48,440 --> 01:25:50,040
Murex, kimchi, and ramyeon.

2608
01:25:51,640 --> 01:25:53,016
Is it different because of the sea breeze?

2609
01:25:53,040 --> 01:25:54,140
It's totally different.

2610
01:25:55,310 --> 01:25:57,510
(He stuffs his mouth with the unique flavor.)

2611
01:25:59,680 --> 01:26:00,719
My goodness.

2612
01:26:00,720 --> 01:26:02,019
- Is it good?
- It's on another level.

2613
01:26:02,020 --> 01:26:03,049
(While everyone is fascinated by the seafood ramyeon)

2614
01:26:03,050 --> 01:26:04,489
Everyone. Earlier,

2615
01:26:04,490 --> 01:26:06,289
