2616
01:26:06,290 --> 01:26:07,319
- Yes.
- Right.

2617
01:26:07,320 --> 01:26:09,430
I think it will be okay to have one of you taste it.

2618
01:26:09,530 --> 01:26:11,230
Are you giving us a cooked crab?

2619
01:26:11,490 --> 01:26:13,029
